content:
Posted: January 6, 2016
Early Access Review
								// BeamNG.drive is a 3D Racing Simulator: //// Schuitje82 - Extended Review //When I made this review the game had been released in Early Access.There is no influence from the maker due to a free key or any other reasons.Title: BeamNG.driveGenre: Race, Simulator,Developer: BeamNG 	Release date: 29 mei 2015 (Early Access)Why I wanted it, and maybe you will too?===============================Personally I love race / car simulator video games.If it's a racing game like Forza or a Sandbox simulator I want to play them all.I've watched some movies and reviews about this game and wanted to know for myself what this game is all about.Yes it's a simulator and oh yeah.... you can crash your car and it’sreally AWESOME!Still, I wanted to try it myself and make a review about it.Core Gameplay:============This is a pure simulator, so if you are looking for a racing game, maybe this is also something for you.You have some different modes to choose from, like Scenarios such as Freeroaming.Scenarios are  for the people who like to have a goal while they play around with the simulator.I must say there are really very many modes made for you to try.For example: Road Race, Jumps, Full Circuit Racing, Rally Croos Long Courses, Destruction Derby (multiplayer) and much more!The Free roaming is really cool for the player who likes to drive around the levels the Dev's made for us.You can choose already from 10 massive levels that you can drive and play through with all the cars that are ready to pickup from the car list.If you think, “What kind of levels?’ for example:You can choose from giant cliff, Derby Arena, Small Island, USA; and East Cost, USA as a Raceway to go high speed.So these modes give you many hours of fun and in the future they will add campaigns for more ways to play.Last option and I think the coolest is the "Add Content" option.What makes this game really cool is that you can add your own levels and mods to it that other people have built for us.Check the MOD section on the online website to see all the crazy and cool things other people have made for this awesome game.http://www.beamng.com/resources/?ingame=2I geot excited after every page seeing what all people have made for this great sanbox simulator !!Graphics:========The first thing that makes this a nice simulator is the graphical part. (In my opinion.)Everything looks really amazing and that was the first thing i noticed about the game that made me want to try it.Not only the roads, but even the tree's a looking amazing. What appeals to me most is the car detail!For example the car interior, engine, and everything else looks really amazing,.aAnd let’s not forget about the damage that can be done to your car!If you crash into a tree, your car’s hood folds like a piece of paper.I think they did a really great job with this aspect of the game!The onOnly thing I think is annoying sometimes: with a small crash even when there isn’t any huge physical damage, your car can get stuck and not be moved / driven.Controls:=======I played the game with my keayboard as well as my Xbox 360 Wireless controller.I can recommend the controller because you have more feeling with it.For example, make sure to remember that  when you take a turn, sometimes your car brakes out and with a controller it is much easier to control and recover the car.I'm happy with the dev's choice for controller support because many games I play in early access does not support this.The cars feltels really weird in the beginning when I played the game, only after some time did I get used to it.Every car feels slightly different, which and still makes it fun to play and try every car that I can choosice from.They did a really good job with the different roads, likeand I mean is whean you go offroad racing.Multiplayer:=========Still this is a early access game, but there are some crazy co-op local co-op things to do.Like destructiiton derby, that is a lot of fune to play with up to 4 players local.I hope the Dev's can add online multiplayer modesmode to this, so we can all drive all together!.Overall:======This a really fun and well madegood and fun Car simulator where  you can have hours of fun!.TheGame game wais only released infrom 2015 and there are allready so many community mods we can try out!.It's a nice project with very much potential to it.... so Dev's keep up the good work.I give this Simulator a 9/10 score.A job well done !!== For more reviews go to www.gamegrin.com ==== Please don't forget to like my reviews ==

